  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Exercise may improve physical capacity and health parameters in Primary Syndrome´s Sjogren,
      Myositis and Takayasu's Arteritis.

      Therefore, this study aims to investigate the role of an exercise training program in
      patients with Primary Syndrome´s Sjogren, Myositis and Takayasu's Arteritis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
