    <intervention_type>Other</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>Exercise training</intervention_name>
    <description>&quot;Sjöegren arm&quot;: 30-60 minutes of combined aerobic and strength exercises, twice a week, moderate intensity.
&quot;Myositis arm&quot;: 30 minutes of resistance training combined partial blood flow restriction, twice a week, low intensity.
&quot;Takayasu's arteritis arm&quot;: 30-50 minutes of aerobic, twice a week, moderate intensity.</description>
